Definition: polypeptide hormone secreted by the mucous lining of the stomach
Example: when peptides and amino acids are present in the small intestine the secretion of gastric acid is stimulated
Synonyms: gastrointestinal_hormone, polypeptide, hormone, secreted, by, the, mucous, lining, of, stomach, when, peptides, and, amino, acids, are, present, in, small, intestine, secretion, gastric, acid, is, stimulated
Category: noun.body
